      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so my doctor prescribed me some diazepam to help me finally get some sleep because my anxiety has been crazy lately. i was wondering though, if i have like one glass of red wine with dinner, does that make the diazepam work better? i feel like it might help me relax even faster so i can actually pass out.",
